    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You possess to the blessing of Hydaelyn, the mothercrystal of Etheirys. This blessing tends to make you able to withstand even the most dire of straits and grants you power to light your darkest hour.</p><p>You gain a Limit Rank of 1 and the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.actions.Item.zJ3Jakto3oqJTLZR]{Limit Break} action. Additionally, you choose one of the below Limit Styles and gain a 1st rank Limit Break feat from that style, which can be found here.</p><ul><li><strong>Commando</strong> Limit Breaks which feature powerful single-target damage abilities.</li><li><strong>Medic</strong> Limit Breaks which focus on healing damage and recovering status effects.</li><li><strong>Ravager</strong> Limit Breaks which feature room-clearing area of effect abilities.</li><li><strong>Saboteur</strong> Limit Breaks which center around debilitating enemies.</li><li><strong>Sentinel</strong> Limit Breaks which favor defending oneself and protecting allies.</li><li><strong>Synergist</strong> Limit Breaks which focus on providing buffs to allies.</li></ul><p>At 5th level, 10th level, and 15th level, your Limit Rank increases by 1 and you choose an additional Limit Break from the Limit Ranks available to you. At 20th level, your Limit Rank increases by 1 but you do not get another Limit Break.</p>",
